What does (-2, Target Word, +2) mean?

It does not mean subtraction or addition.

It indicates the position relative to the target word.

| Position | Meaning                       |
| -------- | ----------------------------- |
| -2       | Second word before the target |
| -1       | First word before the target  |
| Target   | Current word to predict       |
| +1       | First word after the target   |
| +2       | Second word after the target  |


